# === HITBOX ===
hitbox circle 1.0,1.0 0.75 z 0-1.5

# Glow of cosmic cracks bleeding into surroundings
circle 1.0,1.0 0.95 gradient-radial #a080ff #1a0828 0.25

# Outer irregular fragment silhouette (petrified, weathered)
poly 0.95,0.08 1.45,0.14 1.82,0.36 1.92,0.78 1.88,1.22 1.78,1.62 1.52,1.86 1.12,1.94 0.68,1.88 0.32,1.72 0.12,1.42 0.08,0.96 0.16,0.54 0.42,0.22 texfill polyhaven/stone_wall 0.9
